GateDocument.TextWithNodes: Call for Papers & Participation DESIGN AND MANAGEMENT OF DATA WAREHOUSES ( DMDW'99 ) Workshop W 3 at CAiSE- 99 , Heidelberg , Germany June 14 - 15 , 1999 We cordially invite practitioners and researchers from the data warehousing area and related areas to participate in the workshop DMDW'99 . The workshop is held in conjunction with CAiSE'99 . More information on the workshop is available at http : / / sunsite . informatik . rwth-aachen . de / DMDW 99 / The deadline for submitting papers is April 15 . We especially invite experience reports from suppliers and appliers of data warehouse technology . Participation requires registration via the CAiSE organization at http : / / www-i 5 . informatik . rwth-aachen . de / conf / caise 99 / SSKregistration . html Participants can register to the workshop only ( early bird : DM 240 ) or for the whole conference ( early bird : DM 690 + DM 60 ) . If you are active in the area , then you should consider to submit a paper or participate in the workshop . Heidelberg is an attractive city that is easy to reach from Frankfurt . Kind regards , DMDW'00 organizing committee Stella Gatziu Manfred Jeusfeld Martin Staudt Yannis Vassiliou ( PC chair ) - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
